00:18:15.680 --> 00:18:18.560
How we do it is through differential builds.

00:18:18.900 --> 00:18:26.140
We have created our own runtime, which is called ZRX, and differential builds mean that we are only rebuilding what changed.

00:18:26.220 --> 00:18:32.180
So, for instance, if you only change the page title, only that page and all instances where the page title is used are being rebuilt.

00:18:32.400 --> 00:18:35.520
